local speedSlider = PTab:CreateSlider({Name="[ üìè ] ‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏£‡πá‡∏ß‡πÉ‡∏ô‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏¥‡πà‡∏á", Range={1,1000}, Increment=1, Suffix=" Speed", CurrentValue=32, Flag="RunSpeed", Callback=function(val) runSpeed=val if superSpeed then humanoid.WalkSpeed=runSpeed end end})
 
